r capital management inc private company information  bloomberg july    am et capital markets company overview of r g niederhoffer capital management inc snapshot people company overview r g niederhoffer capital management inc is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor the firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles it also caters to corporations the firm manages separate clientfocused portfolios it invests in public equity fixed income currency and commodity markets across the globe the firm also invests in derivatives including spot currencies futures contracts forward contracts swaps and options it employs quantitative analysis to make its investments it obtains external research to complement its inhouse research to make its investments r g niederhoffer capital management inc was founded in  and is based in new york city  broadwayth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwniederhoffercom key executives for r g niederhoffer capital management inc mr roy g niederhoffer founder president and director age  mr zinovi levitan director of operations mr ronald bruce graber general counsel and chief compliance officer paul shen head trader compensation as of fiscal year  r g niederhoffer capital management inc key developments rg niederhoffer capital presents at context summits europe  may may   rg niederhoffer capital presents at context summits europe  may  venue hotel w barcelona barcelona spain similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global 