hoffer a professor at john jay the new york times january    the education of a speculator business week retrieved november     a b c d e  nominees  investors choice awards  a b c d roy niederhoffer in memory of elaine niederhoffer eulogy for my mom daily speculations april  retrieved november    william g bailey  the encyclopedia of police science taylor  francis  the police family from station house to ranch housearthur niederhoffer elaine niederhoffer lexington books national library of australia catalogue  retrieved november     elaine eisenberg niederhoffer obituary the new york times april    john jay supporters are champions of justice john jay college of criminal justice alumni news march   a b c d e f niels kaastruplarsen qa roy niederhoffer veteran hedge fund manager and top traders unplugged host niels kaastruplarsen talks to the founder of rg niederhoffer capital management cta intelligence december    marvin lebowitz obituary  manalapan nj home news tribune november    richard jay alexander parlor night debuts in manhattan with michael mcelroy the broadway inspirational voices and plenty of broadway royalty broadway world june    andy newman long island high school alumni recall connection to the confederate flag the new york times june    great neck public schools showcase of achievement great neck record april    tandy radio shack trsmodeli roms download games alien invasion the old computer retrieved november     interface age vol  mcpheters wolfe  jones   jack b rochester and john gantz  the naked computer a laypersons almanac of computer lore wizardry personalities memorabilia world records mind blowers and tomfoolery w morrow  george blank the national trs computer show private audiences with top programmers creative computing vol  number  p  august   george blank programmer of the month softside november   ginger szala december  trader profile street stories roy niederhoffer filtering out the noise for profits futures magazine retrieved november 