 the option to register for online banking at the time you open your first gs bank account if you did not register for online banking at the time of account opening simply register for access now what fees are associated with my online savings account there are no transaction fees at gs bank how can i withdraw money there are two ways you can withdraw money from your online savings account through gs bank electronic transfer transfer funds to domestic accounts you own at another financial institution that have been linked to your gs bank account and that we have verified are owned by you you can also initiate an electronic transfer from another financial institution wire transfer send a domestic wire transfer to accounts you own at other financial institutions by calling us toll free at save  monday through friday am to pm ct wires requested after pm ct will be considered received on the next business day in most circumstances we will only allow a transfer of funds from your account at gs bank to an account you own at another financial institution it may take one  to three  business days to process your request wire transfers are subject to our wire transfer security procedures you will need to provide the gs bank routing transit number the wire transfer address and your account number routing transit number rtn     wire transfer address                 goldman sachs bank usa  west street new york ny  there is a limit of six withdrawals or transfers in a monthly statement period for online savings accounts note there is an outgoing transfer limit of  per transfer when the transfer is initiated online if you need to withdraw more than  please call us toll free at save  monday through friday am to pm ct how many withdrawals can i make each month there is a limit of six withdrawals or transfers in a monthly statement period for online savings accounts what are my online transfer limits there is an outgoing transfer limit of  per transfer when the transfer is initiated 